hadiths[29]{hadithnumber,text}:
706,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney narsinghaa bajwane ka irada farmaya, aur naaqoos (ghanti) (ki tayyari) ka hukm diya to wo tarash liya gaya. (uskey baad) Hazrat Abdullah bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ko khuwab aaya. wo farmatey hain : mujhey (khuwab mein) do sabz (hare) kapdey pehney huye eik mard nazar aaya, wo naaqoos (ghanti) uthaey huye tha. mainey usey (khuwab mein) kaha : Allah key bandey ! naaqoos bechogey? usney kaha : aap iska kya kerengey? mainey kaha : main iskey sath namaz ka aelan karunga. usney kaha main aap ko is sey behtar chiz na bataaun? mainey kaha : wo kya hai? usney kaha : aap yun kahin (اللَّهُ أَكْبَرُ اللَّهُ أَكْبَرُ) ''Allah sab sey bada hai, Allah sab sey bada hai.'' (اللَّهُ أَكْبَرُ اللَّهُ أَكْبَرُ), ''Allah sab sey bada hai, Allah sab sey bada hai.'' (أَشْهَدُ أَنْ لَا إِلَهَ إِلَّا اللَّهُ), ''main gawahi deta hun ke Allah key siwa koi mabood nahin. (أَشْهَدُ أَنْ لَا إِلَهَ إِلَّا اللَّهُ), ''main gawahi deta hun ke Allah key siwa koi mabood nahin. (أَشْهَدُ أَنَّ مُحَمَّدًا رَسُولُ اللّٰهِ), ''main gawahi deta hun ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Allah key Rasool hain."" (أَشْهَدُ أَنَّ مُحَمَّدًا رَسُولُ اللّٰهِ), ''main gawahi deta hun ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Allah key Rasool hain.'' (حَيَّ عَلَى الصَّلَاةِ), ''namaz ki taraf aao."" (حَيَّ عَلَى الصَّلَاةِ), ''namaz ki taraf aao.'' (حَيَّ عَلَى الْفَلَاحِ), ''kamiyabi ki taraf aao.'' (حَيَّ عَلَى الْفَلَاحِ), ''kamiyabi ki taraf aao. (اللَّهُ أَكْبَرُ اللَّهُ أَكْبَرُ), ''Allah sab sey bada hai, Allah sab sey bada hai.'' (لَا إِلَهَ إِلَّا اللّٰهُ), ''Allah key siwa koi mabood nahin. Hazrat Abdullah bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) (bedaar huye to ghar sey) nikley aur Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huye, aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko apna khuwab sunaya , unhoney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! mujhey eik aadmi nazar aaya jo do sabz (hare) kapdey pehney huye tha uskey paas naaqoos (ghanta) tha. (is tarah) puri baat batai. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tumharey sathi ney eik khuwab dekha hai. (phir Abdullah bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) sey farmaya :)  tum Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) key sath masjid mein jao aur unhen ye alfaz batlao. aur Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) (un alfaz key sath buland aawaz sey) aelan kar den kyonkey tumhari nisbat un ki aawaz buland hai.  main Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) key sath masjid mein gaya. main unhen (azaan key alfaz) batata gaya aur wo (uskey mutabiq) Azan kehtey gaey. Hazrat Abdullah bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : Hazrat umr bin Khittab (Raziallahu anhu) ney (azaan ki) aawaz suni to wo bhi ghar sey bahar tashrif ley aaye aur arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! qism hai Allah ki mujhey bhi aisa hi khuwab aaya hai jaisa inhen ( Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ko) aaya hai. Hazrat Abu-Bakar Hakmi (Ibne-Maja key Shaikh) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Abdullah bin Zaid Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) ney uskey mutalliq ye she'r kahey hain : mujh ko Azan sikhai merey Rab ney ehsan huwa khas Rab qadeer ka. bheja sikhaaney apney farishtey ko teen raat, rutba badhaaney apney is Bashir ka. wo teen raat aa key sikhata raha mujhey, Aejaaz yun badhta raha terey faqir ka (tarjama ashaar Molana Abdul Hakeem Khan Akhtari Shaahjahanpuri)."
707,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney logon sey mashwara kiya kyonkey namaz (baa jamaat) key liye (aaney mein) unhen mushkil pesh aati thi (kyonkey eik hi waqt jama nahin ho paatey they). haazirin ney narsinghey ka zikr kiya lekin aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney yahudiyon (sey muwaafiqat) ki wajeh sey usey na pasand farmaya. phir unhoney naaqoos (ghanti) ka zikr kiya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney nasara ki wajeh sey usey na pasand farmaya. usi raat eik Ansari Sahaba Hazrat Abdullah bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ko aur Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ko) khuwab mein Azan dikhai gaee. Ansari Sahaba Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key paas raat ko aaye (aur apna khuwab sunaya) chunanche Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ko hukm diya aur unhoney Azan kahi. eik riwayat mein hai ke Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ney subah ki Azan mein in alfaz ka izafa farmaya : (اَلصَّلَاةُ خَیْرٌ مِّنَ النَّوْمِ), ''namaz neend sey behtar hai.'' Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney isey qaaim rakha. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : aey Allah key Rasool ! mujhey bhi us jaisa khuwab aaya tha lekin wo mujh sey sabqat ley gaey."
708,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Maheereez (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, wo (bachpan mein) yatim honey ki wajeh sey Hazrat Abu-Mahzoora bin Maeer (Raziallahu anhu) key zere-kafalat rahey they. jab unhoney ibne Maheereez (Rahimahullah) ko Sham bheja to unhoney Abu-Mahzoora (Raziallahu anhu) sey kaha, chacha jaan ! main Sham ja raha hun, (wahan) mujh sey aap ki Azan key barey mein sawal kiya jaeyga (lihaza mujhey masla suna aur samjha dijiye). Hazrat Abu-Mahzoora (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : main chand afrad key sath safar par rawana huwa. raastey main eik maqam par (thehrey wahin) Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key padaaw mein Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key muazzan ney Azan di. hamney bhi muazzan ki aawaz suni. us waqt hum log aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey bargashta they. hum muazzan ka mazaq udatey huye buland aawaz sey uski naqal utaarney lagey. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney hamari aawaz suni to chand afrad ko hamari taraf bhej diya. unhoney hamein Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key samney la bithaya. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum mein sey wo kon hai jiski aawaz mujhey (ziyada) buland sunai di thi? sab key sab logon ney meri taraf ishara kar diya. aur un ki baat durust thi (waaqaee main sab sey buland aawaz tha). Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney un sab ko chhod diya aur mujhey rok liya aur farmaya : utho, Azan do. main khada to ho gaya lekin (us waqt meri kaifiyat ye thi ke) mujhey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey aur aap key us hukm sey intehai nafrat mehsus ho rahi thi. (har haal mein) main Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key samney khada huwa , aur Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney mujhey khud (eik eik kalima kar key) Azan sikhai. farmaya : kaho (اللَّهُ أَكْبَرُ اللَّهُ أَكْبَرُ اللَّهُ أَكْبَرُ اللَّهُ أَكْبَرُ أَشْهَدُ أَنْ لَا إِلَهَ إِلَّا اللَّهُ أَشْهَدُ أَنْ لَا إِلَهَ إِلَّا اللَّهُ أَشْهَدُ أَنَّ مُحَمَّدًا رَسُولُ اللَّهِ أَشْهَدُ أَنَّ مُحَمَّدًا رَسُولُ اللَّهِ), phir farmaya : buland aawaz sey kaho (أَشْهَدُ أَنْ لَا إِلَهَ إِلَّا اللَّهُ أَشْهَدُ أَنْ لَا إِلَهَ إِلَّا اللَّهُ أَشْهَدُ أَنَّ مُحَمَّدًا رَسُولُ اللَّهِ أَشْهَدُ أَنَّ مُحَمَّدًا رَسُولُ اللَّهِ حَيَّ عَلَى الصَّلَاةِ حَيَّ عَلَى الصَّلَاةِ حَيَّ عَلَى الْفَلَاحِ حَيَّ عَلَى الْفَلَاحِ اللَّهُ أَكْبَرُ اللَّهُ أَكْبَرُ لَا إِلَهَ إِلَّا اللَّهُ), jab mainey puri Azan keh li to mujhey bula kar eik thaili di, is mein kuchh chaandi thi, iskey baad aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney apna haath Abu-Mahzoora (Raziallahu anhu) key sar par rakha, phir unkey chehrey par pheraa, phir unkey seeney par, phir unkey jigar par yahan tak key Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka haath Abu-Mahzoora (Raziallahu anhu) ki naaf tak ja pahuncha, phir Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah tujhey barkat dey, aur tujh par barkat nazil farmaaey. mainey arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! aap mujhey Makka mein Azan deney par muqarrar farmaeyngey? irshad huwa : haan, mainey tumhen muqarrar kiya. (us doran main) merey dil mein Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey jitni nafrat thi sab khatam ho chuki thi, (balke) wo sab ki sab Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki mohabbat mein tabdeel ho chuki thi. main Makka mein Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key muqarrar karda governer Hazrat Itaab bin Usaid (Raziallahu anhu) key paas gaya, main unkey paas Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key hukm sey Azan deta raha. Abdul-Azeez ney kaha : Abdullah bin Maheereez ki tarah mujhey us shakhs ney bhi khabar di jisney Abu-Mahzoora ko paya."
709,"Hazrat Abu-Mahzoora (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mujhey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Azan key unnis kalimaat, aur iqaamat key satrah kalimaat sikhaey. Azan ye hai : ( اللّٰهُ أَكْبَرُ اللّٰهُ أَكْبَرُ اللّٰهُ أَكْبَرُ اللّٰهُ أَكْبَرُ أَشْهَدُ أَنْ لَا إِلَهَ إِلَّا اللّٰهُ أَشْهَدُ أَنْ لَا إِلَهَ إِلَّا اللّٰهُ أَشْهَدُ أَنَّ مُحَمَّدًا رَسُولُ اللّٰهِ أَشْهَدُ أَنَّ مُحَمَّدًا رَسُولُ اللَّهِ أَشْهَدُ أَنْ لَا إِلَهَ إِلَّا اللّٰهُ أَشْهَدُ أَنْ لَا إِلَهَ إِلَّا اللّٰهُ أَشْهَدُ أَنَّ مُحَمَّدًا رَسُولُ اللّٰهِ أَشْهَدُ أَنَّ مُحَمَّدًا رَسُولُ اللّٰهِ حَيَّ عَلَى الصَّلَاةِ حَيَّ عَلَى الصَّلَاةِ حَيَّ عَلَى الْفَلَاحِ حَيَّ عَلَى الْفَلَاحِ اللّٰهُ أَكْبَرُ اللّٰهُ أَكْبَرُ لَا إِلَهَ إِلَّا اللّٰهُ), ''Allah sab sey bada hai, Allah sab sey bada hai. Allah sab sey bada hai, Allah sab sey bada hai. main gawahi deta hun ke Allah key siwa koi mabood nahin, main gawahi deta hun ke Allah key siwa koi mabood nahin. main gawahi deta hun ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Allah key Rasool hain, main gawahi deta hun ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Allah key Rasool hain. main gawahi deta hun ke Allah key siwa koi mabood nahin, main gawahi deta hun ke Allah key siwa koi mabood nahin. main gawahi deta hun ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Allah key Rasool hain, main gawahi deta hun ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Allah key Rasool hain. namaz ki taraf aao, namaz ki taraf aao. kamiyabi ki taraf aao, kamiyabi ki taraf aao. Allah sab sey bada hai, Allah sab sey bada hai. Allah key siwa koi mabood nahin. aur iqaamat key satrah kalimaat ye hain :(اللّٰهُ أَكْبَرُ اللّٰهُ أَكْبَرُ اللّٰهُ أَكْبَرُ اللّٰهُ أَكْبَرُ أَشْهَدُ أَنْ لَا إِلَهَ إِلَّا اللّٰهُ أَشْهَدُ أَنْ لَا إِلَهَ إِلَّا اللّٰهُ أَشْهَدُ أَنَّ مُحَمَّدًا رَسُولُ اللّٰهِ أَشْهَدُ أَنَّ مُحَمَّدًا رَسُولُ اللّٰهِ حَيَّ عَلَى الصَّلَاةِ حَيَّ عَلَى الصَّلَاةِ حَيَّ عَلَى الْفَلَاحِ حَيَّ عَلَى الْفَلَاحِ قَدْ قَامَتْ الصَّلَاةُ قَدْ قَامَتْ الصَّلَاةُ اللّٰهُ أَكْبَرُ اللّٰهُ أَكْبَرُ لَا إِلَهَ إِلَّا اللّٰهُ)''Allah sab sey bada hai, Allah sab sey bada hai. Allah sab sey bada hai, Allah sab sey bada hai. main gawahi deta hun ke Allah key siwa koi mabood nahin, main gawahi deta hun ke Allah key siwa koi mabood nahin, main gawahi deta hun ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Allah key Rasool hain, main gawahi deta hun ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Allah key Rasool hain. namaz ki taraf aao , namaz ki taraf aao , kamiyabi ki taraf aao , kamiyabi ki taraf aao. namaz khadi ho gaee , namaz khadi ho gaee . Allah sab sey bada hai. Allah sab sey bada hai. Allah key siwa koi mabood nahin."
710,"Hazrat Saad Qurz (Raziallahu anhu) jo Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key muazzan they, un sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ko kanon mein ungliyan dalney ka hukm diya, aur farmaya : is sey tumhari aawaz buland ho jaeygi."
711,"Hazrat Abu-Juhaifa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main maqam abtah par Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa aur aap eik surkh kheme mein tashrif farma they. Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) (kheme sey) nikley, unhoney Azan di, aur Azan key doran mein (daain baain) ghoomey , aur apni ungliyan apney kanon mein dalin."
712,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Muazzanon ki gardanon par musalmanon ki do chizon ki zimmedari hai, un ki namaz aur unkey rozey."
713,"Hazrat Jabir bin Samura (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) Azan ko waqt sey muakhkhar (der) nahin kartey they, albatta iqaamat mein baaz oqaat (waqt) takheer kar detey they."
714,"Hazrat Usman bin Abi Al-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney mujhey sab sey aakhir mein jo wasiyat farmaai thi, wo ye thi ke main aisa muazzan muqarrar na karun, jo Azan deney ki ujrat wasul karey."
715,"Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney mujhey Fajr ki namaz mein taswib ka hukm diya, aur Isha ki namaz mein taswib sey mana farmaya."
716,"Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke wo Fajr ki namaz ki ittilaa deney key liye Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huye to malum huwa ke aap abhi aaram farma rahey hain. Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : (اَلصَّلَاۃُ خَیْرٌ مِّنَ النَّوْمِ , اَلصَّلَاۃُ خَیْرٌ مِّنَ النَّوْمِ), ''namaz neend sey behtar hai, namaz neend sey behtar hai. tab ye kalima Fajr ki Azan mein muqarrar kar diya gaya, phir isi par amal jari raha."
717,"Hazrat Ziyad bin Haris Sudaai (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : main eik safar mein Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath tha. aap ney mujhey hukm diya to mainey Azan di. (jamaat key waqt) Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ney iqaamat kehna chahi to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qabila banu Sudaai key aadmi ney Azan di hai aur jo koi Azan dey, wohi iqaamat kahey."
718,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab muazzan Azan dey to jis tarah wo kehta hai, isi tarah tum bhi kaho."
719,Hazrat Ummul-mominin Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) un ki baari key din aur raat unkey yahan tashrif farma they. us doran main aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney muazzan ko Azan detey suna to Ummul-mominin ney suna ke aap ney bhi isi tarah kaha jis tarah muazzan ney kaha.
720,Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tum Azan suno to isi tarah kaho jis tarah muazzan kehta hai.
721,"Hazrat Saad bin Abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney muazzan ki Azan sun kar ye alfaz kahey : (وَأَنَا أَشْهَدُ أَنْ لَا إِلَهَ إِلَّا اللَّهُ وَحْدَهُ لَا شَرِيكَ لَهُ وَأَشْهَدُ أَنَّ مُحَمَّدًا عَبْدُهُ وَرَسُولُهُ رَضِيتُ بِاللَّهِ رَبًّا وَبِالْإِسْلَامِ دِينًا وَبِمُحَمَّدٍ نَبِيًّا) ""aur main bhi gawahi deta hun ke akeley Allah key siwa koi mabood bar-haq nahin, uska koi shareek nahin, aur main gawahi deta hun ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uskey bandey aur uskey Rasool hain. main Allah key rab honey par, Islam key Deen honey par aur Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key Nabi honey par razi hun."" uskey gunah maaf ho jaeyngey."
722,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney Azan sun kar ye dua padhi : (اللّٰهُمَّ رَبَّ هَذِهِ الدَّعْوَةِ التَّامَّةِ وَالصَّلاَةِ الْقَائِمَةِ آتِ مُحَمَّدًا الْوَسِيلَةَ وَالْفَضِيلَةَ وَابْعَثْهُ مَقَامًا مَحْمُودًا الَّذِى وَعَدْتَهُ), ''aey Allah ! aey is kamil pukar aur qaaim honey wali namaz key Rab ! Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko wasila aur fazilat ata farma aur unhen us maqame Mehmood par faaiz farma jis ka tu ney un sey wada farmaya hai.'' qiyamat key din uskey haq mein shafaat ki ijazat mil jaeygi."
723,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Sasaa (Rahimahullah) (jo Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ki kafalat mein they) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : mujh sey Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : jab tum jangal mein ho to Azan buland aawaz sey diya karo kyonkey mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey ye irshad suna hai : jo bhi jin , insan , darkht ya patthar us (muazzan) ki aawaz suneyga, (qiyamat ko) uskey haq mein gawahi dega."
724,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna hai : muazzan ki aawaz jahan tak pahunchti hai, wahan tak uski maghfirat kar di jati hai. har tar aur khushk chiz uskey haq mein duaaey maghfirat karti hai aur (azaan sun kar) namaz key liye hazir honey waley key liye pachchees nekiyan likhi jati hain, aur uskey do namazon key darmiyan key gunah maaf kar diye jatey hain."
725,"Hazrat Muawiya bin Abu-Sufiyaan (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qiyamat key din muazzanon ki gardanen sab sey lambi hongi."
726,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Azan wo log den jo ziyada behtar (nek) hon, aur tumhen namaz wo afrad padhaein jo Quran padhney waley (haafiz aur aalim) hon."
727,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney sawab ki niyat sey saat saal (musalsal) Azan di, Allah Taala uskey liye jahannam sey najat likh deta hai."
728,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs baara baras tak Azan deta hai, uskey liye jannat wajib ho jati hai, aur uskey liye rozaana Azan key iwaz saath nekiyan likhi jati hain aur har iqaamat key iwaz tees nekiyan likhi jati hain."
729,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Sahaba kiram Raziallahu anhum ko kisi aisi chiz ki talash thi jis ko alamat bana kar wo namaz ki ittilaa dey saken. (aakhir kaar) Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ko hukm diya gaya ke Azan mein do baar kalimaat kahin aur iqaamat main eik eik baar kahen."
730,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye hukm diya gaya tha ke Azan key kalimaat do-do baar kahin aur iqaamat key kalimaat eik-eik baar.
731,"Hazrat Saad bin Ammar bin Saad sey riwayat hai, unhoney apney walid sey aur unhoney unkey dada sey riwayat ki ke Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ki Azan dohri aur iqaamat ikahri hoti thi."
732,"Hazrat Abu-Raafey (Raziallahu anhu), jo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key ghulam they, sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ko Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki mojudgi mein Azan key kalimaat do-do baar aur iqaamat key kalimaat eik-eik baar kehtey dekha."
733,"Janab Abu-Sha'shaa (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) key sath masjid mein bethey huye they. (isi beech mein) muazzan ney Azan kahi. eik aadmi masjid sey utha aur chal diya. Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) uski taraf dekhtey rahey yahan tak key wo masjid sey nikal gaya. tab Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya is shakhs ney Hazrat Abul-Qaasim (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki hukm aduli ki hai."
734,"Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs masjid mein Azan ho janey key baad masjid sey nikal gaya, wo kisi majburi ki wajeh sey nahin nikla aur wapis aaney ka irada bhi nahin rakhta to wo munafiq hai."
